objects.generator

Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • objects.generator.Vertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasName

    public class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
implements HasName
    Class Vertex vertex is an object for Dijkstra. We used vertex for searching shortest route with name of ancestor. Vertex has space object because it can be planet or factory.
    Author:
    Jiří Lukáš
